PREFIX legal: <https://www.w3.org/ns/legal#>
PREFIX locn: <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

ASK WHERE { 
		?this rdf:type epo:ReviewProcedureInformationProvider .
		?this epo:playedBy / legal:registeredAddress / locn:thoroughfare ?value . }
query.title: VI.4.4.2 - Postal address

query.description: “VI.4.4.3 - Town” in SF corresponds to “BT-513 Organisation City” in eForms. The corresponding XML element is /TED_EXPORT/FORM_SECTION/F23_2014/COMPLEMENTARY_INFO/ADDRESS_REVIEW_INFO/TOWN. The expected ontology instances are epo: epo:AgentInRole (from CL1) / org:Organization (from CL2) /  locn:Address / rdf:langString .
